---
title: Creamy Pea Curry with spinach and cannellini beans
description: This creamy pea curry is inspired by a number of different cuisines. That's why it's bursting with flavour, fabulously spicy and filled with an array of different vibrant vegetables.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R21_W46_IE_IEXQVV17786-2_Main__1high-0ab33201.jpg
